name: Fishy Feast
description:
Fishy Feast is a crazy minigame in which you have to eat smaller fish and try not to get eaten to ultimately dominate the sea!

Sometimes there is a bug when you cannot eat anything. Get eaten by the biggest fish and play again, it will be fixed. Apologies for this bug.

Controls: WASD/Arrow keys

This game was developed for the Mini Jam 108: Seaside
